{"tid":2419218,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方扯到五日前放映會踩場衝突  兩人認罪案情倒模監警會","createTime":"2021-02-23T07:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T08:10:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"095db8f1218fa735fe80a71bfd07860c0dd1e498","tid":2419218,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/3SHDFE3TSVAMFGEO3FRNAYFHLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2F3SHDFE3TSVAMFGEO3FRNAYFHLI%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv36HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=2d5ae899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2F3SHDFE3TSVAMFGEO3FRNAYFHLI%2F&h=dd454d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/3SHDFE3TSVAMFGEO3FRNAYFHLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n控方扯到五日前放映會踩場衝突 <br />\n兩人認罪案情倒模監警會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tGlnA3FrM-L-9ZjjAx1mvrI0xTo=/2537x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLIPXEMJQFG7DL7QACEJ6R75QM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtGlnA3FrM-L-9ZjjAx1mvrI0xTo%3D%2F2537x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLIPXEMJQFG7DL7QACEJ6R75QM.jpg&h=f88b197b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■7.21當日大批白衣人追打市民，但控方案情指白衣人數目較黑衣人少。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7.21白衣人暴動案，其中「懵良」林觀良及「肥林」林啟明承認參與暴動，據控方撰寫的案情，將7.21事件扯到事發前五日在元朗舉行的反修例放映會，有「持相反意見人士」踩場「發生衝突」，跟着有網民呼籲案發當日集會，有關案情與監警會去年5月發表的7.21調查報告內容幾乎完全相同；惟控方未有「抄足」所有內容，包括將白衣人改成「持相反意見人士」，亦未有像監警會交代公眾集會最終有否如期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傷者名單無何桂藍 有嚇到肚痛者<br />\n<br />\n控方在兩名認罪被告的案情，甫開首扯到2019年7月16日傍晚的放映會，指有部份支持反修例示威者舉行公開放映會，有持相反意見人士到場與示威者發生衝突，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上述來自控方案情的首兩段，竟與監警會去年5月15日發表的《2019年7月21日（星期日） 元朗事件》報告內容幾乎完全相同，其中「部份反對《逃犯條例》修訂草案的示威者在元朗攸北街的休憩處舉行公開放映會」、「&hellip;&hellip;但衝突未有演變成暴力事件。當警務人員到達現場後，雙方便散去。」兩句的字眼、句式及標點完全一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指黑衣人多白衣人一倍<br />\n<br />\n控方並無完全搬字過紙，它刪去放映會指控警暴、將白衣人改為「持相反意見人士」、刪去網上指事件涉及黑社會，亦未有像監警會交代公眾集會最終有否如期舉行，也沒寫號召「保護元朗家園」的網上訊息警告會對示威者使用暴力的內容。<br />\n<br />\n案情續指，2019年7月21日晚上，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有白衣人用金屬垃圾桶蓋、木棍及藤條毆打黑衣人，有人遭圍毆，當中包括一名記者。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案情指懵良及肥林聯同其他白衣人，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ap7iwzjo0V48HcRcDjitJkiTcF4=/649x2090/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7BADCH7IORGNTGORCXEU4N7G4Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAp7iwzjo0V48HcRcDjitJkiTcF4%3D%2F649x2090%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7BADCH7IORGNTGORCXEU4N7G4Q.png&h=c423aa5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"081860e1cf97d08ab74237b83758d3a26674c275","tid":2419218,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:50:58.000Z","msg":"Hea撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcac97f0b7f0ea2baadccc3fed423a40e3fa301e","tid":2419218,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"鳩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}